mayor: Ahoy hoy?
mayor: Oh? You need to turn a crank?
mayor: But the crank is out of oil?
mayor: And the store is closed?!?
mayor: I understand your struggle, my friend. As a fellow crank connosieur, I will help you!
mayor: I would give you the key to the store, but you see.......It fell down the village well.
mayor: You'll need a rope and a magnet to take it out.